%% HireSphere — Container diagram (actual deployment shape)
flowchart TB
  subgraph Client
    SPA[React Vite SPA<br/>Role portals + AuthContext]
  end

  subgraph Server
    API[HireSphere.API<br/>ASP.NET Core controllers<br/>JWT + RBAC policies]
    Workers[In-process workers<br/>Notification outbox processor]
  end

  subgraph Data
    DB[(SQL Server / LocalDB<br/>HireSphereDev)]
    FS[Local secure file store<br/>metadata in DB]
  end

  SPA -->|HTTPS/HTTP JSON| API
  API --> DB
  API --> FS
  API --> Workers
  Workers --> DB
